1
00:00:01,090 --> 00:00:03,300
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:00:03,300 --> 00:00:07,090
Well, we somehow managed to 
stop the Dragon Chain Cannon.

3
00:00:07,090 --> 00:00:10,850
We managed somehow once 
I rushed onto the scene!

4
00:00:10,850 --> 00:00:12,390
What're you trying to prove?

5
00:00:12,390 --> 00:00:14,860
By the way, you're heavy, Lucy.

6
00:00:14,860 --> 00:00:17,120
I could see you being like, 0.05 tons.

7
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:19,040
Don't measure it in tons!

8
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:56,160
Oww!

9
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,560
Aye...

10
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:03,170
And why did you crash land when 
you were only carrying one person?

11
00:02:03,170 --> 00:02:04,660
'Cause you're heavy, Lucy...

12
00:02:04,660 --> 00:02:07,550
You just <i>have</i> to keep 
pushin' that, don't you?

13
00:02:07,930 --> 00:02:08,940
Where's Erza?

14
00:02:09,530 --> 00:02:11,530
With the other Erza...

15
00:02:16,250 --> 00:02:17,200
Enemies?

16
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,100
Where?

17
00:02:29,050 --> 00:02:30,880
Those Who Are Alive!

18
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,660
They just keep comin' out of the woodwork.

19
00:02:35,660 --> 00:02:37,900
Please stop, everyone!

20
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:39,260
I guess we have no choice.

21
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,990
Bastards!

22
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:51,200
Why?

23
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:53,360
Why are they aiming at Happy and Carla?

24
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:57,480
We've turned most of the Exceeds 
that ran for it into lacrima!

25
00:02:58,730 --> 00:03:00,800
All that's left are those two.

26
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:03,740
Now stand still, so we can turn you 
into our kingdom's magic power!

27
00:03:05,790 --> 00:03:11,250
So you don't give a damn what happens to the 
Exceed, if it's for your own magic power?

28
00:03:13,860 --> 00:03:16,420
Is that what the humans 
are like on this world?

29
00:03:19,130 --> 00:03:22,340
I ain't gonna let you hurt my 
friends, you filthy bastards!

30
00:03:23,730 --> 00:03:25,300
Save the Exceed!

31
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:28,900
I met Gajeel on my way here.

32
00:03:28,900 --> 00:03:31,350
Things have moved pretty far along.

33
00:03:31,350 --> 00:03:33,970
Gajeel? You mean the informant?

34
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:37,690
It's true that his info 
is always reliable, but...

35
00:03:38,490 --> 00:03:44,080
The Kingdom is trying to sacrifice 
the Exceed, Earthland, and us,

36
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:47,550
and make the entire world 
theirs to do as they please!

37
00:03:47,830 --> 00:03:50,700
We can't let them get away with that, can we?

38
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:55,270
But the Royal Army has a huge 
amount of magic power...

39
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,980
Could we win if we fought them?

40
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:02,920
Furthermore, the Royal Army has 
a number of very powerful foes.

41
00:04:03,300 --> 00:04:07,010
Do we even have a chance 
of winning against them?

42
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:15,290
Heaven's Wheel, Trinity Sword!

43
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:17,810
Gravity Core!

44
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:26,410
Blue Crimson!

45
00:04:32,620 --> 00:04:33,630
Requip!

46
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:39,710
Venus Photon Slicer!

47
00:04:41,190 --> 00:04:42,510
Runesave!

48
00:04:43,220 --> 00:04:45,020
She cut through the magic?

49
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:47,030
Silfarion!

50
00:04:53,700 --> 00:04:55,810
You're mine!

51
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:01,940
What?

52
00:05:05,670 --> 00:05:10,160
I propose that we wait until the battle 
between the Exceed and the Kingdom is over!

53
00:05:11,050 --> 00:05:14,250
They'll both be tired 
out, and when we show up,

54
00:05:14,250 --> 00:05:16,750
we could take them both out! How about that?

55
00:05:16,750 --> 00:05:19,560
Well, that method might have merit.

56
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:22,930
In other words, make the 
most of the opportunity.

57
00:05:22,930 --> 00:05:26,810
Or, we could ally with the Kingdom.

58
00:05:27,130 --> 00:05:29,430
We put the Kingdom in our debt,

59
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:32,030
and get them to recognize us.

60
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:36,510
That's right. This might be a chance 
to make up with the Kingdom.

61
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:40,240
Way to go, Juvia-chan! You're so smart!

62
00:05:39,470 --> 00:05:40,750
Stay away!

63
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:42,700
I hate how you smother me!

64
00:05:45,290 --> 00:05:46,680
That won't do.

65
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:52,920
We should know better than anyone 
that the Kingdom isn't so weak!

66
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:58,610
I think the same thing!

67
00:05:58,610 --> 00:06:03,380
Far from making up with them, I bet 
we'd be treated even worse than before!

68
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:07,480
Droy's suggestion is also not possible.

69
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:13,300
When the Exceed are wiped out, the Kingdom 
will surely move on to their next ambition!

70
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:18,470
They'll suppress anyone who opposes them, 
and we'll fall into a new dark age!

71
00:06:18,780 --> 00:06:21,630
We'll lose the one opening we have!

72
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:25,900
This is no time for humans to 
be fighting with the Exceed!

73
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:42,240
You have no chance of winning!

74
00:06:43,910 --> 00:06:46,710
Everyone's suffering from 
lack of magic power...

75
00:06:47,580 --> 00:06:51,090
...but their king sure has 
plenty all for himself.

76
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:57,290
It's only natural for a 
king to tax his people.

77
00:06:57,910 --> 00:07:02,970
Droma Anim is constantly absorbing 
magic power from the entire world...

78
00:07:02,970 --> 00:07:05,680
The ultimate magical weapon!

79
00:07:06,100 --> 00:07:09,370
That's also the reason 
it is a forbidden weapon.

80
00:07:09,370 --> 00:07:13,570
Once activated, I have a duty to 
win, for the sake of the world!

81
00:07:13,570 --> 00:07:15,230
For the world?!

82
00:07:15,230 --> 00:07:17,620
You're just stealin' magic for yourself!

83
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:19,700
How can you say that with a straight face?!

84
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:26,500
See, we joined a guild so that we could live.

85
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:30,210
I might not know much 'bout this world.

86
00:07:31,210 --> 00:07:35,970
But for the sake of all the living things 
of this world, I will defeat you!

87
00:07:35,970 --> 00:07:39,090
I-I'm scared, I really am!

88
00:07:39,090 --> 00:07:42,750
Maybe we shouldn't do 
anything and just hide...

89
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:47,820
Honestly speaking, as long as I can live 
together in peace with Bis Bis, I'll be happy.

90
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:51,900
Yeah... We shouldn't be searching 
out danger ourselves.

91
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:54,370
What a bunch of spineless wimps!

92
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:58,580
When the Exceeds are all gone, 
they'll come after us next!

93
00:07:59,290 --> 00:08:02,110
Everyone knows that, Lucy.

94
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:07,630
But no matter what you say, everyone 
knows how fearsome the Kingdom is.

95
00:08:08,850 --> 00:08:12,800
Plus, Fairy Tail here doesn't 
have any magic power left...

96
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:15,510
We can only long-distance transfer once more.

97
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:19,760
If we jump into this fight, 
there's no pulling out.

98
00:08:23,530 --> 00:08:25,600
Gate of the Lion, I open thee!

99
00:08:25,980 --> 00:08:26,530
Loke!

100
00:08:29,770 --> 00:08:31,030
Sorry to keep you waiting.

101
00:08:34,900 --> 00:08:36,530
Carla, this way.

102
00:08:36,530 --> 00:08:37,780
Happy...

103
00:08:40,410 --> 00:08:41,710
Fire!

104
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:44,250
Magic Bullets?

105
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:48,040
Happy, watch out!

106
00:08:49,260 --> 00:08:50,250
Carla!

107
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:53,060
Carla!

108
00:08:55,050 --> 00:08:57,200
Crap, I hit an Exceed!

109
00:08:57,200 --> 00:09:00,430
Fool! That's going to be our magic power!

110
00:09:01,130 --> 00:09:05,380
Carla, hang in there! Carla!

111
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:15,420
Happy, take Carla someplace safe!

112
00:09:15,420 --> 00:09:16,990
Thanks, Loke.

113
00:09:22,970 --> 00:09:24,750
I'm not done yet!

114
00:09:33,860 --> 00:09:37,720
I think everyone's said their 
opinion. It's about time to decide.

115
00:09:44,340 --> 00:09:46,750
I want people to hear one last thing.

116
00:09:48,170 --> 00:09:53,930
Right now the Fairy Tail from Earthland is 
fighting the Kingdom, risking their lives!

117
00:09:54,650 --> 00:10:00,930
Earthland's Natsu, Gray, 
myself, and everyone else!

118
00:10:16,350 --> 00:10:19,840
At this rate... everyone is going to die...

119
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:27,050
I'm not done yet! I can't be defeated here!

120
00:10:27,050 --> 00:10:29,520
We can't just stand back and 
watch while they're killed!

121
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:33,900
We have to cut open a path to 
our world's future ourselves!

122
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:38,100
Natsu and Erza should still be fighting!

123
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:41,700
We can't give up before they do!

124
00:10:42,110 --> 00:10:46,090
We're the only ones who can 
stand against the Kingdom now!

125
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:48,760
We can do it! We can win!

126
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:50,780
Because we're...

127
00:10:50,780 --> 00:10:52,680
Why? Because we're...

128
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:55,880
...Fairy Tail wizards!

129
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:59,840
It's no use... We're just too outnumbered...

130
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:22,220
Someone... save us!

131
00:11:34,170 --> 00:11:35,850
W-What's this?

132
00:11:35,850 --> 00:11:38,000
It's like a tree that's moving on its own...

133
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:39,380
What's that?

134
00:11:47,970 --> 00:11:50,930
No way... Those guys who only ever run away?

135
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:04,910
Here we go!

136
00:12:05,740 --> 00:12:08,580
We'll show you the power 
of the bonds of friendship!

137
00:12:11,830 --> 00:12:14,290
It's the Edolas Fairy Tail!

138
00:12:15,640 --> 00:12:18,790
Sorry 'bout that. Were we late, Earth-Lucy?

139
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:21,230
Edo-Lucy...

140
00:12:30,930 --> 00:12:32,310
Go!

141
00:12:32,310 --> 00:12:34,890
Pummel the Royal Army!

142
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:36,980
Natsu, go for it!

143
00:12:36,980 --> 00:12:40,870
Sure! The Earthland Fairy Tail is fighting,

144
00:12:40,870 --> 00:12:42,490
so we'll fight, too!

145
00:12:47,470 --> 00:12:49,080
Can you stand, Earth-Lucy?

146
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,240
Double Lucy...

147
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,200
Thank you...

148
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:53,410
Me? And look at your clothes!

149
00:12:53,410 --> 00:12:54,140
Strip down!

150
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:55,120
Put some clothes on!

151
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:57,850
I can't believe there are two Grays!

152
00:12:57,850 --> 00:12:59,540
Juvia's in a pickle!

153
00:12:59,540 --> 00:13:01,380
Ooh, I wish I were them...

154
00:13:01,630 --> 00:13:04,140
You're me, so why can't you feel what I do?

155
00:13:04,140 --> 00:13:06,840
Just look at my beloved Juvia-chan!

156
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:09,110
Beloved Juvia-chan?!

157
00:13:09,110 --> 00:13:11,890
Juvia-chan, I love you!

158
00:13:11,890 --> 00:13:13,350
Argh, shut up!

159
00:13:13,350 --> 00:13:16,180
We can't lose either, Al Al!

160
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:17,980
Let's go, Bis Bis!

161
00:13:17,980 --> 00:13:19,060
This is our...

162
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:20,430
...power of love!

163
00:13:20,430 --> 00:13:22,510
Yeehaw!

164
00:13:22,510 --> 00:13:24,530
Nobody's stronger than us!

165
00:13:24,530 --> 00:13:26,000
Prepare yourselves!

166
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:28,450
Make sure to show up Lucy, boys!

167
00:13:28,450 --> 00:13:30,080
Heck yeah!

168
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:35,040
Let me show you the strongest 
power in Fairy Tail!

169
00:13:39,950 --> 00:13:42,900
<i>I'm</i> the strongest!

170
00:13:46,310 --> 00:13:47,940
W-Wow...

171
00:13:47,940 --> 00:13:49,510
He's even faster than me!

172
00:13:50,590 --> 00:13:52,750
Gray is drooling all over Juvia?

173
00:13:52,750 --> 00:13:55,570
Plus, Jet and Droy are 
contending for the strongest?

174
00:13:55,570 --> 00:13:57,520
There's so much completely backwards!

175
00:13:57,520 --> 00:14:02,280
Look, Carla. Fairy Tail came to rescue us.

176
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:09,230
Our feelings are making this world change.

177
00:14:09,780 --> 00:14:11,360
Natsu, hang in there!

178
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,350
Thank you, Lisanna-chan!

179
00:14:13,350 --> 00:14:16,330
We're Shadow Gear, the strongest of them all!

180
00:14:16,330 --> 00:14:17,520
Al Al!

181
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:19,220
Let's go, Bis Bis!

182
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:23,830
No matter where you go, our 
guild's making trouble...

183
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:34,470
Scarlet!

184
00:14:34,470 --> 00:14:36,390
Knightwalker!

185
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,670
Still even, after all this.

186
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:48,990
Even? I don't think so.

187
00:14:48,990 --> 00:14:53,070
You still haven't experienced the 
ultimate form of the Ten Commandments!

188
00:14:58,870 --> 00:15:00,620
Holy Lance, Ravelt!

189
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:04,630
A holy lance forged by the 
greatest blacksmith in Edolas.

190
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:08,710
Its attack brings ultimate destruction 
that resounds out into the land.

191
00:15:15,580 --> 00:15:17,100
Armadura Faerie!

192
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:18,310
Fairy Armor!

193
00:15:19,030 --> 00:15:23,350
I need hardly explain why it 
bears the name of our guild.

194
00:15:24,160 --> 00:15:26,580
So you're saying that's 
your strongest magic, then?

195
00:15:26,860 --> 00:15:29,190
Fascinating... Have at me!

196
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:49,300
M-My Ravelt...

197
00:15:50,470 --> 00:15:52,300
M-My armor...

198
00:15:55,420 --> 00:15:59,260
With that attack, the floating 
island can no longer stay afloat.

199
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:02,490
Neither of us has any magic power left.

200
00:16:02,490 --> 00:16:04,600
And yet I will strike you down!

201
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:11,070
Why, you...

202
00:16:13,490 --> 00:16:19,080
No matter how many times you stand, 
you will never be able to defeat me!

203
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:22,290
Those with magic power will rule the world!

204
00:16:22,290 --> 00:16:25,190
That's something this world requires!

205
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:29,710
Stop twistin' logic to justify your actions!

206
00:16:29,710 --> 00:16:31,250
You dolt!

207
00:16:31,250 --> 00:16:36,340
I don't know whether it requires it or not, 
but I do know I'm gonna bust that thing up!

208
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:38,390
Roar of the Sky Dragon!

209
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:48,480
Would you please refrain from 
wasting all the magic power?

210
00:16:48,830 --> 00:16:52,270
Because all your magic power is mine!

211
00:16:52,270 --> 00:16:55,690
Don't even joke about that! 
My magic power is my own!

212
00:16:55,690 --> 00:16:57,560
It ain't no one else's but mine...

213
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:01,790
Pillar of the Iron Dragon!

214
00:17:10,230 --> 00:17:15,720
Your magic power, your very lives... 
They're all mine for the taking!

215
00:17:22,100 --> 00:17:24,400
Like hell they are!

216
00:17:27,230 --> 00:17:29,540
Juvia-chan, so cool!

217
00:17:29,540 --> 00:17:34,220
Get off me! Try taking a page out of 
that other Gray's book and strip down!

218
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:39,600
You bastards! Don't you realize 
what you're doing is wrong?

219
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:41,200
W-Well...

220
00:17:41,660 --> 00:17:46,570
They should realize.  There should be some 
people against what the Kingdom is doing here.

221
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:52,170
If they disobey, they'll be killed, 
so they have no choice but to fight!

222
00:17:52,410 --> 00:17:55,130
War is just so tragic.

223
00:17:55,950 --> 00:17:59,840
I would much rather have a tea 
party with everyone, but no!

224
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:04,390
Even so, we have no choice 
but to counterattack them.

225
00:18:04,390 --> 00:18:09,200
By the way, Earth-Lucy... Is the 
guy with glasses your boyfriend?

226
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:11,320
No, he's not! He's...

227
00:18:11,320 --> 00:18:13,400
Do we look that way to you?

228
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:16,760
You're also Lucy, so I guess you can tell.

229
00:18:16,760 --> 00:18:18,950
I hate playboys!

230
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:21,800
Happy...

231
00:18:23,660 --> 00:18:25,470
Edolas's Wendy!

232
00:18:25,900 --> 00:18:27,980
You're Exceeds, right?

233
00:18:28,970 --> 00:18:31,460
It'll be okay... Shall I stay with you?

234
00:18:31,940 --> 00:18:34,640
Thanks, but I'm fine.

235
00:18:34,640 --> 00:18:36,660
Happy is here for me, so...

236
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:50,330
I'll be nearby, and if anything 
happens, I'll protect you. Rest easy.

237
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:56,510
Edolas's Wendy is also kind.

238
00:18:56,510 --> 00:18:57,380
Yeah!

239
00:18:59,820 --> 00:19:03,610
I can't lose, for the sake of eternal energy!

240
00:19:03,950 --> 00:19:08,790
For your accursed "eternity", how many 
sacrifices have been made in your "now"?

241
00:19:11,450 --> 00:19:14,460
Oppress and steal! Coerce and steal!

242
00:19:14,460 --> 00:19:16,970
Hate the other! Destroy the other!

243
00:19:16,970 --> 00:19:19,260
That's what humans do!

244
00:19:20,590 --> 00:19:23,890
People should love people more!

245
00:19:24,900 --> 00:19:27,570
They stand up for the people they care about!

246
00:19:28,120 --> 00:19:30,980
They pick up swords for those who shed tears!

247
00:19:31,550 --> 00:19:36,060
Can't you hear this world screaming 
in agony, Knightwalker?!

248
00:19:36,650 --> 00:19:41,360
The screams of the world? I'm sure 
I can feel them more than you!

249
00:19:41,850 --> 00:19:45,440
The magic drying up... 
And because of that, I...

250
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:48,910
No! When I say the world, 
I mean the living things!

251
00:19:51,130 --> 00:19:53,770
This world is heading toward oblivion.

252
00:19:53,770 --> 00:19:57,710
It is a world running out of 
magic, plunging toward its death!

253
00:19:57,710 --> 00:20:00,210
A person from Earthland like 
you could never understand!

254
00:20:00,210 --> 00:20:03,450
The anxiety, fear, despair 
of having magic disappear!

255
00:20:03,450 --> 00:20:07,510
We can't survive unless we get 
an eternal source of magic power!

256
00:20:09,170 --> 00:20:11,110
But we're alive, aren't we?

257
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:11,680
Right now!

258
00:20:12,370 --> 00:20:14,640
We don't have any magic 
power, but we're alive!

259
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:20,150
Look at us! We've both used it all up!

260
00:20:20,570 --> 00:20:23,110
And yet, we aren't dead!

261
00:20:23,520 --> 00:20:27,570
We have the strength to overcome 
the weakness and the fear!

262
00:20:28,430 --> 00:20:30,700
That's what it means to be alive!

263
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:36,630
Hear this, Erza! Inside of you is the same 
frailty and evil that lies within me!

264
00:20:36,630 --> 00:20:40,120
Therefore, I know you hold a 
heart that can love others!

265
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:43,130
Listen to the voices of the 
living, with your entire heart!

266
00:20:43,930 --> 00:20:45,830
This is... Erza?

267
00:20:46,540 --> 00:20:48,160
Me?

268
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:50,420
Speak with your true voice!

269
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:55,070
What's this...?

270
00:20:57,750 --> 00:20:58,940
Tears...?

271
00:20:59,370 --> 00:21:01,160
You are not alone.

272
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,980
What just happened?

273
00:21:06,330 --> 00:21:07,980
Something fell down, damn it!

274
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:09,530
Erza?

275
00:21:18,650 --> 00:21:21,660
I don't have any strength left to move...

276
00:21:21,660 --> 00:21:23,460
But, you're alive.

277
00:21:24,810 --> 00:21:28,930
I couldn't match you... You win, Scarlet.

278
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:34,390
This battle is not one that could 
be won or lost. We're both Erza.

279
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:38,250
I see...

280
00:21:43,730 --> 00:21:44,730
This is...

281
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:48,780
The chamber that creates the Anima?

282
00:21:51,220 --> 00:21:53,470
Prince, what in the world are you...

283
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:56,910
I observed Earthland for a long time.

284
00:21:57,600 --> 00:22:00,780
There was strife, but it 
was a wonderful world.

285
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:04,170
I am sure they'll accept this...

286
00:22:04,170 --> 00:22:07,960
Prince! You can't mean... That's just...

287
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:09,930
That is far too radical!

288
00:22:09,930 --> 00:22:13,650
This is the only way to 
rid this world of war.

289
00:22:14,040 --> 00:22:17,480
I will create a world where people 
can be open with each other.

290
00:22:18,700 --> 00:22:20,420
I will throw the Anima into reverse...

291
00:22:21,050 --> 00:22:24,380
...and rid this world of all its magic power!

292
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:59,930
Damn it... It's just a fake 
dragon but it's pretty tough!

293
00:23:59,930 --> 00:24:02,860
I guess they don't call it an 
ultimate weapon for nothing.

294
00:24:02,860 --> 00:24:06,020
Damn... It's a real pain that 
magic doesn't work on it.

295
00:24:06,020 --> 00:24:09,270
But we have three Dragon Slayers on our side!

296
00:24:09,270 --> 00:24:10,830
No way we'd lose!

297
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:13,550
Okay! Let's go another round!

298
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:16,550
Next time: I'm Standing Here!

299
00:24:17,040 --> 00:24:19,390
But Natsu, do you have any magic power left?

300
00:24:19,390 --> 00:24:21,100
Even if I didn't, I'd do it somehow!

301
00:24:21,580 --> 00:24:24,230
I'll show you the stubborn 
pride of Fairy Tail!

302
00:24:24,230 --> 00:24:26,460


